      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im in tokyo right now for work and i think im just exhausted from the flight. my left arm feels kinda heavy and tingly, like it's not quite mine, and my speech sounds a bit thick when i talk to people. is it normal to feel like this when you're super tired and dehydrated?",
